<item>
            <title>[SEC-2961] Configuring AuthenticationManagerBuilder with GlobalAuthenticationConfigurerAdapter fails</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2961</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I already &lt;a href=&quot;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/29683098/spring-security-java-config-configuring-authenticationmanagerbuilder-with-globa&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;posted this issue on stackoverflow&lt;/a&gt; some time ago, but I thought I better file this as a bug here, too.&lt;/p&gt;

